{"tid":2282181,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《浴火的少女畫像》導演Céline Sciamma 新戲開拍","createTime":"2020-11-11T16:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T07:52:33.000Z","uid":157092,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6410b2b0f86ecd30249d3e62410465f76f41d2cc","tid":2282181,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T16:02:53.000Z","msg":"Celine Sciamma Shooting New Movie &lsquo;Petite Maman&rsquo; in France<br />\n<a href=\"https://variety.com/2020/film/news/celine-sciamma-petite-maman-filming-1234825938/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2020%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fceline-sciamma-petite-maman-filming-1234825938%2F&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Auwu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=fc988b10\" target=\"_blank\">https://variety.com/2020/film/news/celine-sciamma-petite-maman-filming-1234825938/</a><br />\n<br />\nFollowing on the heels of critical smash &ldquo;Portrait of a Young Lady on Fire,&rdquo; Celine Sciamma has just started shooting her next film, &ldquo;Petite maman,&rdquo; in Paris.<br />\nAlthough the plot is under wraps, the movie will deal with childhood and will star two eight-year-old kids, according to Les Inrocks magazine.<br />\nSciamma is re-teaming with her regular producer B&eacute;n&eacute;dicte Couvreur at Lilies Films, and&nbsp;MK2 Films, which will handle international sales on the film. Headlined by Adele Haenel and No&eacute;mie Merlant, &ldquo;Portrait of a Young Lady on Fire&rdquo; was sold around the world by MK2 Films after competing at Cannes and winning the best screenplay award. On top of winning a flurry of prizes and a Golden Globe nomination, the French film performed well at the overseas box office, notably in the U.K.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Petite maman&rdquo; will mark Sciamma&rsquo;s fifth film. The popular French screenwriter-director previously shed light on childhood in her critically acclaimed film &ldquo;Tomboy&rdquo; in 2011. The movie won a prize in Berlin.<br />\n&ldquo;Petite maman&rdquo; also brings back key crew members such as the seasoned cinematographer Claire Mathon, who won a Cesar award for her work on &ldquo;Portrait of a Young Lady on Fire.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nAside from her career as a filmmaker, Sciamma is also a popular screenwriter whose credits include the Oscar-nominated animated feature &ldquo;My Life as a Zucchini.&rdquo; She also co-wrote Jacques Audiard&rsquo;s next film &ldquo;Les Olympiades&rdquo; with Audiard and L&eacute;a Mysius (&ldquo;Ava&rdquo;). &ldquo;Les Olympiades&rdquo; started shooting in September in Paris."},{"pid":"33801d0459f29158441d2ec18dc843ebc622c32a","tid":2282181,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T16:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5fdb556dc8b98002f7f265f6f7cc6f6dfa62ee","tid":2282181,"uid":166405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T16:36:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3caeb6661d2e0070d2f8636099b3d21e0b29c7d","tid":2282181,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T16:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c89bc4021f83df6c43176ec2b1f245bc2982c1","tid":2282181,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T17:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa